,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:15:36.000Z","msg":"我之前都係5月尾6月頭去克羅地亞玩左11日<br />\n路線係Zagreb&gt;Dubrovnik&gt;Hvar&gt;Split&gt;Zadar&gt;16湖&gt;Zagreb<br />\n<br />\nDubrovnik 我都係住山上airbnb 個海景好靚<br />\n同埋pass都抵 包撘巴士同上城牆一次"},{"pid":"98ce46bbfd0f5b06058faf134e4b5ff4ca4014c8","tid":170510,"uid":85475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/25/091714_2c58a229b16cf915108bae1ca0666010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F25%2F091714_2c58a229b16cf915108bae1ca0666010.jpg&h=00977cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十六湖真係好靚 我總共行左兩次full route <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c44e7b537b097d838be7743f5cf49be7da63d98","tid":170510,"uid":47876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"留個靚名 有性趣"},{"pid":"3104c6b82c8e53022120935308eabd6126b5944f","tid":170510,"uid":71323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"個人認為Croatia嘅Rovinj唔應該skip"},{"pid":"5d6ad4ae3b3d441602637099629f8890b5730815","tid":170510,"uid":85475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人認為Croatia嘅Rovinj唔應該skip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果陣係<br />\nLjubljana - Rovinj - Pula - Rijeka (宿Rijeka)<br />\nRijeka - Zagreb - 16 湖 <br />\n<br />\n咁玩<br />\n<br />\n搭巴士搭到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9edc669382be34d3e29292346b160acca465fb8","tid":170510,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:53:41.000Z","msg":"下個月經Budapest <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed563e7f6df339c163dcd02cbaf7af1470abc71","tid":170510,"uid":85475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime