moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5025a7aa4b97ff37260779084df744cf3ef7675b","tid":170510,"uid":96071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十六湖可以day trip 返 Zagreb</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該都唔會再返Zagreb會搭巴士去Split啦，anyway唔該巴打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9452659cc802c7fc42146bbe02eed8c3010356","tid":170510,"uid":96071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遲啲5月尾至6月中會去克羅地亞同Budapest玩14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，請問有咩特別要注意，因為第一次去，想準備充足啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望各位可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行程大約係<br />\n<br />\nHk&gt;zagreb&gt;Budapest&gt;Zagreb&gt;Zadar&gt;16湖&gt;split&gt;Dubrovnik<br />\n<br />\n唔去Hvar係因為揾到個喺Split出發嘅day tour去blue cave ，個行程包埋去Hvar，所以唔去了<br />\n<br />\n唔該哂咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你最尾係邊到返香港? Dubrovnik?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打算玩到落Dubrovnik再搭內陸機返返Zagreb，check過內陸機好似都係貴巴士百幾二百但快勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207ef838fb57a67982238a61a5ade6b002286295","tid":170510,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十六湖可以day trip 返 Zagreb</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該都唔會再返Zagreb會搭巴士去Split啦，anyway唔該巴打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以去埋Trogir<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順路都幾靚架"},{"pid":"f58d001fc45c053edaeeb09d9088569b6d1eebed","tid":170510,"uid":96071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:39:31.000Z","ms