5T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十六湖可以day trip 返 Zagreb</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該都唔會再返Zagreb會搭巴士去Split啦，anyway唔該巴打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以去埋Trogir<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順路都幾靚架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能唔夠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  宜家嘅行程都係啱啱好夠玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改去黑山"},{"pid":"a473b7d7a7d3f5b402fdabf097c868c0d9f1fc52","tid":170510,"uid":96071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>克羅地亞真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n物價相比其實歐洲國家低<br />\n又少大陸人 我係hostel遇到好多韓妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係貪佢地方靚物價唔高同無乜蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n去到十六湖一定撞到旅行團😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6月都未算係旺季掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望少啲蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6c6d96774c53c57d159bf978a3b643e3dd76b8","tid":170510,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"上年九月去左克羅地亞。<br />\n<br />\n如果幾個friend 去，可以租車。租棍波車share 一定比去tour 平。克羅地亞d 路幾好揸。<br />\n<br />\nhvar 我覺得其實幾舒服，如果唔去曬左<br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞d 機場細，飛去布達佩斯會貴兼曬時間。其實你可以考慮下去 Ljubljana. 克羅地亞附近都有d 野睇。又或者由 Dubrovnik 入黑山。<br />\n<br />\n係Dubrovnik 有好多水上活動同潛水。如果有牌，你應該去潛水。d 水極清。<br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞好多韓妹。d 韓國人好鐘意去克羅地亞。"},{"pid":"16eacf7297a47aa4b29ba5a0d011851d2b98d408","tid":170510,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"我九年前去，多日本人"}]}